text: Amblymora pseudoconferta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939. It is known from the Celebes Islands.BioLib.cz - Amblymora pseudoconferta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Amblymora Category:Beetles described in 1939
